1
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:15,240
Only then did I realize the drug was highly unstable

2
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:18,640
and could cause severe adverse effects.

3
00:00:19,039 --> 00:00:22,600
But the Wang Group discovered this drug.

4
00:00:23,039 --> 00:00:24,480
They're morally bankrupt

5
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:25,559
and driven purely by profit.

6
00:00:25,559 --> 00:00:27,120
They tried to force my parents to hand it over.

7
00:00:29,480 --> 00:00:30,559
My parents refused.

8
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:34,520
So they murdered my parents

9
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:38,359
and had me framed and imprisoned.

10
00:00:39,799 --> 00:00:40,960
What nonsense are you spouting?

11
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:43,799
This is slander!

12
00:00:43,799 --> 00:00:44,600
I'll sue you!

13
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:46,840
If what I said was false,

14
00:00:47,479 --> 00:00:49,200
why are you so worked up, Young Mr. Wang?

15
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:50,560
Triggered?

16
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:53,600
If you don't want your daughter to die,

17
00:00:54,119 --> 00:00:55,320
get the hell out of here now.

18
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:58,640
Then I might spare this little thing.

19
00:01:00,439 --> 00:01:03,240
While Ruojin was attending the wedding as promised,

20
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:05,239
what do you think I was doing?

21
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,959
Da Long wasn't by his side.

22
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,719
That was our way in.

23
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:29,519
You eat first, I need the wrapper.

24
00:01:29,519 --> 00:01:30,400
Thanks.

25
00:01:33,519 --> 00:01:34,000
Stop right there!

26
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,359
No!

27
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:41,599
Don't do this, Daddy!

28
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,319
Yixin, are you okay?

29
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:54,560
Daddy!

30
00:01:54,799 --> 00:01:56,079
Yixin is fine.

31
00:01:56,359 --> 00:01:59,319
Big Brother Da Long took great care of me.

32
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,799
Come on, let's go with Daddy.

33
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,360
Wang Wenhao!

34
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:21,840
You incited murder, kidnapping, extortion,
and ruined a Family of TCM practitioners.

35
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,039
You ran illegal experiments.

36
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,319
The evidence is ironclad.

37
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:30,919
This time,

38
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,000
you won't escape.

39
00:02:35,599 --> 00:02:36,000
Dad!

40
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:37,400
Say something, Dad!

41
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,120
None of this was my doing!

42
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:41,960
I truly never imagined

43
00:02:42,439 --> 00:02:44,719
you'd commit such evil behind my back.

44
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,719
You unfilial son!

45
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:48,879
Dad!

46
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,840
I'm your own son!

47
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,000
Why are you doing this to me?

48
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,919
A child's misdeeds are the father's fault.

49
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:57,360
That you've turned out like this,

50
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,960
much of the blame lies with me.

51
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,000
Just go and serve your time.

52
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,240
Wang Wenhao,

53
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,360
you're suspected of murder and other crimes.

54
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:05,800
Dad!

55
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,479
Come with us.

56
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:07,759
Dad, save me!

57
00:03:08,599 --> 00:03:08,960
Dad!

58
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,199
Dad!

59
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:22,039
Satisfied now?

60
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,120
Wang Chengren.

61
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,439
You murdered my parents.

62
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,520
This is only the beginning.

63
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:31,800
But I've got to hand it to you.

64
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:35,479
You'd even throw your own son under the bus.

65
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,680
You may have escaped today,

66
00:03:38,919 --> 00:03:40,120
but you won't escape tomorrow.

67
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:41,960
The next one

68
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,879
will be you.

69
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:48,319
I harmed your parents?

70
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,159
Ren Feifan,

71
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,719
your parents died because of you.

72
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,400
You're the real reason.

73
00:03:55,719 --> 00:03:58,479
Don't you feel even the slightest guilt?

74
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:15,800
Ruojin

75
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:17,720
It's been hard on you.

76
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,639
Hey, hey, he's proposing!

77
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,480
Xu Ruojin

78
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,279
Will you marry me?

79
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,319
Say yes! Marry him!

80
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:45,600
Marry him! Marry him!

81
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,160
Marry him! Marry him!

82
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,040
Yes, I will.

83
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:18,439
The grand hall shines in splendid silks

84
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:20,519
Fair day, fine scene, music resounds

85
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:22,920
Today we raise our cups to kin and friends

86
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:25,800
True love unites a perfect pair

87
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:28,279
Wonderful!

88
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,399
Bravo!

89
00:05:40,199 --> 00:05:40,680
Hold on

90
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,759
Are we really using Wang Wenhao's wedding?

91
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,720
Only a fool turns down a freebie

92
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:51,959
The money we save will all go to you and our daughter

93
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:57,879
But we haven't collected the gift money yet

94
00:05:58,519 --> 00:05:59,079
That's right

95
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,920
Congratulations.

96
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:21,759
You finally got Wang Wenhao locked up.

97
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:24,680
Congratulations to you too.

98
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,000
Your wife and daughter are safe.

99
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:29,319
I...

100
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:29,720
You...

101
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:32,839
You go first.

102
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:35,079
I came to thank you.

103
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:36,560
And also...

104
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:38,199
to say goodbye.

105
00:06:39,879 --> 00:06:41,720
Are you leaving Beishi?

106
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:46,879
My editor loved the Wang family story.

107
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:49,240
So I got transferred to Gangshi.

108
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:51,920
Congratulations.

109
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,920
That's a promotion, isn't it?

110
00:06:54,839 --> 00:06:55,639
Feifan.

111
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:57,759
Are you really married?

112
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,240
Yes.

113
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:04,120
We crashed Wang Wenhao's wedding yesterday.

114
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:04,800
And got married.

115
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,560
But later on,

116
00:07:06,759 --> 00:07:08,079
I'll still hold a proper ceremony.

117
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,639
I want to give Ruojin a perfect ending.

118
00:07:11,279 --> 00:07:13,759
Make sure you come when I invite you.

119
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,079
Do you really love her?

120
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,759
Or is it because she had your child?

121
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,000
Our paths diverge,

122
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,759
we won't meet again.

123
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,680
We won't meet again.

124
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,120
Are you a ghost?

125
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,680
Sneaking around without a sound.

126
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,439
Hero Ren,

127
00:07:51,279 --> 00:07:53,120
you sure have a lot of female admirers.

128
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,800
Ruojin even had a daughter with you,

129
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,720
and raised her all on her own.

130
00:07:59,319 --> 00:08:00,439
I'm warning you,

131
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:03,680
you'd better rein in that wandering heart.

132
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,120
Or else I...

133
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,959
What did I ever do to deserve this?

134
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,079
Here's the prescription.

135
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,560
Go to the back to get it filled.

136
00:08:31,319 --> 00:08:32,000
Okay, thank you.

137
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:39,840
Next.

138
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:03,519
Recently,

139
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,480
many citizens have mysteriously developed

140
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,039
strange symptoms of bleeding
from the mouth and nose.

141
00:09:07,039 --> 00:09:08,240
It has caused significant panic.

142
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:11,120
Experts are currently studying the patients.

143
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:36,200
The child's symptoms are a bit severe

144
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:38,120
but he should recover, don't worry

145
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:39,879
When will it be my turn?

146
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:41,840
Let me take a look

147
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,519
Please examine me

148
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:44,399
Hold it down

149
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:45,360
Press here

150
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:47,200
Wait for me outside

151
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,240
Keep holding it

152
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:51,399
Doctor

153
00:09:51,399 --> 00:09:52,320
Sir, sir

154
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,440
Help, doctor!

155
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:55,559
There are still many people waiting outside

156
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:57,159
What illness do they actually have?

157
00:09:57,159 --> 00:09:59,200
Their pulses show no major abnormalities

158
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,559
but their symptoms

159
00:10:00,559 --> 00:10:01,519
are very similar to the patients

160
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:02,600
we saw in Wang Wenhao's lab

161
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,279
but theirs are more complex and severe

162
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:07,440
Could it be this isn't over yet?

163
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:10,279
Wang Wenhao isn't the only one behind it.

164
00:10:10,799 --> 00:10:11,799
Let's take care of them first

165
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:13,159
Why isn't it my turn yet?

166
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:17,279
Hello, have you eaten anything unusual lately?

167
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:20,200
Have you eaten anything unusual recently?

168
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:23,879
Hello?

169
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,080
You have to answer our questions

170
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,519
so we can treat you

171
00:10:26,519 --> 00:10:27,480
Is your stomach hurting?

172
00:10:28,279 --> 00:10:29,759
Where does it hurt, sir?

173
00:10:31,559 --> 00:10:31,960
Head

174
00:10:32,399 --> 00:10:33,840
Does this hurt, sir?

175
00:10:35,639 --> 00:10:36,159
Sir

176
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:38,879
Sir!

177
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:40,960
Sir!

178
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,679
Give me your hand

179
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:57,679
How is it?

180
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,080
The condition is under control for now

181
00:11:04,519 --> 00:11:05,679
but we have to treat the root cause

182
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,600
To truly cure it,

183
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:13,039
we have to find the source of the illness

184
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:17,279
Mr. Wang, the drug's formula has been changed

185
00:11:17,279 --> 00:11:19,200
Excellent. Release it to the market

186
00:11:20,639 --> 00:11:22,679
But the aconitine in it is highly toxic

187
00:11:23,039 --> 00:11:23,720
I'm afraid

188
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,360
Afraid of what? Just do it

189
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:42,559
Why aren't you asleep this late?

190
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:45,600
I can't sleep

191
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:47,080
I wanted to keep you company

192
00:11:48,159 --> 00:11:48,879
You're so sweet

193
00:11:54,279 --> 00:11:55,480
How's your investigation going?

194
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:59,440
I checked all the patients' connections,

195
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:00,960
and found nothing unusual

196
00:12:02,679 --> 00:12:05,759
I suspect Wang Chengren must be involved

197
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:08,039
but I have no proof

198
00:12:09,639 --> 00:12:11,440
It's fine, we can take our time investigating.

199
00:12:19,919 --> 00:12:21,559
What's that? It smells so nice

200
00:12:24,279 --> 00:12:26,360
Perilla, mint, clove

201
00:12:26,919 --> 00:12:27,559
and also

202
00:12:28,399 --> 00:12:29,759
the moxa you made back then

203
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:32,320
You still have it?

204
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:32,639
Mm-hm

205
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,039
It's getting late

206
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,799
Go back and rest first

207
00:12:45,039 --> 00:12:46,799
I'll head back after finishing this

208
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:51,879
Okay, but hurry up too

209
00:12:51,879 --> 00:12:52,679
Don't stay up too late

210
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,200
I'm really leaving now

211
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,440
Hurry up, don't work too late

212
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:01,879
Okay

